{"tid":694118,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不敵黃雨　西九站又漏水","createTime":"2018-06-08T04:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T10:50:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a4558de79498375c49275125d5e0cf9309a8c07b","tid":694118,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T04:53:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180608/20414417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180608%2F20414417&d=akJa0BhxT1CBrAKZ%2F%2FudKaMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=aeb62f04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180608%2F20414417&h=74cecf79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180608/20414417</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月08日 <br />\n<br />\n不敵黃雨　西九站又漏水<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180608/large/18711315.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180608%2Flarge%2F18711315.jpg&h=eed7054e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■西九站<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】試營運的廣深港高鐵西九龍總站在黃色暴雨下再漏水，港鐵稱只是去水渠淤塞，不涉車站結構安全。立法會議員批評高鐵由4月試營運至今已多次漏水，令人質疑工程驗收非常馬虎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n議員斥驗收馬虎<br />\n<br />\n天文台前日在一號戒備信號下發出黃雨警告。港鐵發言人表示，高鐵西九龍總站地下一層前日出現滲水情況，工程人員檢視後，發現滲水是由於接近車站南面入口地面一段去水渠淤塞，雨水積聚於地面去水渠後，倒流入地下一層及在天花位置滲出。工程人員已清理淤塞去水渠，無影響設施或結構安全。<br />\n<br />\n今次已非高鐵首次漏水，4月西九站地下一層售票大堂，因裝電線有雨水經電線槽滲入致假天花漏水。而站內消防系統在驗收時，亦發現個別喉管在壓力測試下有滲水情況。5月18日米埔一段隧道疑因地下水滲漏，導致信號系統不穩，列車試運行需暫停約一小時。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立會議員陳淑莊批評高鐵試營運後不斷漏水，反映港鐵工程驗收非常馬虎。<br />\n<br />\n■記者麥志榮  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n工程師倡鑿開石屎評估<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n工會認主管筆試有提示<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工程師倡鑿開石屎評估<br />\n<br />\n工會認主管筆試有提示<br />\n<br />\n鋼筋造假醜聞　10日8種說法港鐵懵炳變神探「偵破」泛迅為元凶"},{"pid":"2a05c17fbbf5e2b8045d85ae32865456eddc297f","tid":694118,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T04:55:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84e02f0c213f63ebfa7b71f6c855203f7e6f9c96","tid":694118,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"渣架"},{"pid":"504bb2aa846bebfed7f4c73281faf3eafe2ea68f","tid":694118,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T05:00:40.000Z","msg":"黃雨都搞到咁<br />\n黑雨點算"},{"pid":"9e5b33aa6db0a1d970b8e7b868af7dbe8cde9476","tid":694118,"uid":5499,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"504bb2aa846bebfed7f4c73281faf3eafe2ea68f","tid":694118,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T05:00:40.000Z","msg":"黃雨都搞到咁<br />\n黑雨點算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T05:37:02.000Z","msg":"以後唔掛黑雨咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43cac55cb6a7ebfd3c0a2ab2a76ae94c07140afa","tid":694118,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e5b33aa6db0a1d970b8e7b868af7dbe8cde9476","tid":694118,"uid":5499,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"504bb2aa846bebfed7f4c73281faf3eafe2ea68f","tid":694118,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T05:00:40.000Z","msg":"黃雨都搞到咁<br />\n黑雨點算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T05:37:02.000Z","msg":"以後唔掛黑雨咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T05:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ec417eed42c3d601825162c73e5a57885a67ab","tid":694118,"uid":88345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T06:30:39.000Z","msg":"我哋話你知OK，就得㗎啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569e4da59bb34a8c98c9fc6a0a3aec6488e04de7","tid":694118,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc